    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 29</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The second of a three-move combination attack, this works exactly as Sangeki Hissatsu Waza: Nigeki, except as above, the technique can only be used on a target hit by Nigeki with the same weapon within the last five rounds, and you can also make a third attack at a -10<br><br>penalty. All attacks benefit from the same bonuses (as Nigeki), and each hit provokes a Massive Damage save.</p>\n\n\n\n",
